【新聞 CBC】Cigarette packages will be the 'ugliest colour in the world' starting in November 加拿大政府頒布菸盒新規
加拿大政府宣布~半年後最真實醜陋的「菸盒素面包裝」全面上路！官員指出，11月起所有的菸盒與包裝容器都必須採用：1.品牌名稱為統一字體與字級、2.菸盒顏色為噁心的泥棕綠色(俗稱大便色)的素面包裝，同時搭配正反面75%的菸害警示圖文，積極防制青少年開始吸菸，並促成老菸槍戒菸!→加拿大目前有400萬吸菸人口，約占總人口數的17%。→加拿大每年因菸害而死亡達4.5萬人。→加拿大政府目標2035年成為全國吸菸率5%以下的「無菸國家」。※全球已13個國家實施菸品容器素面包裝～包含澳洲、英國、愛爾蘭、法國、挪威、紐西蘭、匈牙利、烏拉圭、泰國、新加坡、土耳其、斯洛維尼亞、加拿大等。※台灣不但沒採用素面包裝，菸品容器警示圖文之面積更只有正反面的35％，落到全球倒數第四名。Cigarettepackageswillbethe'ugliestcolourintheworld'startinginNovemberNewregulationsremovebrandcolours,fontsfrompackagesTheCanadianPress·Posted:May01,20192:42PMET|LastUpdated:9hoursagoCanadiancigarettepackswillhavetobeplain,drabbrownwithstandardizedlayoutsandletteringundernewrulesthatkickinNov.9,HealthCanadasays.Officialssaidplainpackageswillincreasetheimpactofgraphichealthwarningsaboutthedangersofsmoking,keepingthemfromgettinglostamidcolourfuldesignsandbranding.Thegovernmentwantstostopcigarettecompaniesfromusingtheirpacksastinyadsfortheirproducts,insistingevenonasingleshapeanddesignforthepacksthemselves—meaningsoftpacksareout,asarecreativedesignswithbevellededgesandanyotherdistinctivefeatures.MorethanfourmillionCanadiansstillusetobacco—about17percentofthepopulationaged12andover,HealthCanadasays.Thefederal'sgovernmenttobaccostrategyaimstodrivedowntobaccousetofivepercentoftheCanadianpopulationby2035.HealthCanadapickedthesamedarkbrownforthepackagesasAustraliadidforitstobaccoproductsafewyearsago,oneidentifiedbymarketresearchersastheugliestcolourintheworld.SeveralEuropeancountrieshaveusedthecolouraswell."Packageswithdarkercolourswereperceivedtobemore'harmfultohealth'andtheirproducts'hardertoquit,'incontrasttopackageswithlightercolours,"thedepartmentsaidinasummaryoftheplans.Plainpackagingalsoaimstoincreasetheimpactofthegraphicwarnings.HealthCanadasaiditisadopting"themostcomprehensivemeasures"onplainpackaging.HealthCanadasaidtherecouldbeashortageofthenewpacksintheearlygoingasaverylimitednumberofsuppliersretooltomakejustonedesigninsteadofmanydifferentones.TheregulationsreleasedWednesdayalsostandardizethesizeandappearanceofcigarettes,cigarsandotherto